<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-2xl w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto p-4 sm:p-8 shadow-lg mb-5 mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 underline mb-5">
        About Our App
    </h1>
    <p class="text-center text-lg sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-4">
        Welcome to our social media platform, designed to provide a seamless and engaging user experience. Here are the key features and functionalities of our app:
    </p>
    <div class="space-y-8 mt-10">
        <div>
            <p class="font-bold underline text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2">User Registration and Authentication:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside px-4">
                <li class="font-semibold">User Registration: New users can easily sign up by providing their essential details.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">User Login: Registered users can log in securely using their credentials.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">Password Management: Users can reset their passwords in case they forget them.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">Social Media Integration: Users can log in using their existing social media accounts for convenience.</li>
            </ul>
            <hr class="border border-gray-300 my-4">
        </div>
        <div>
            <p class="font-bold underline text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2">User Profile Management:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside px-4">
                <li class="font-semibold">Profile Creation: Users can create a personalized profile with a profile picture and bio.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">Profile Editing: Users can update their profile information anytime.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">Profile Deletion: Users have the option to delete their profiles permanently.</li>
            </ul>
            <hr class="border border-gray-300 my-4">
        </div>
        <div>
            <p class="font-bold underline text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2">Post Management:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside px-4">
                <li class="font-semibold">Create Posts: Users can create new posts, share their thoughts, and upload images.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">Read Posts: View and read posts from other users in the community.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">Update Posts: Users can edit their posts to keep their content up-to-date.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">Delete Posts: Users have the control to delete their posts if they wish.</li>
            </ul>
            <hr class="border border-gray-300 my-4">
        </div>
        <div>
            <p class="font-bold underline text-lg sm:text-xl mb-2">Additional Features:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside px-4">
                <li class="font-semibold">Search Functionality: Easily search for users and posts within the platform.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">User Interaction: Like, comment, and share posts to engage with other users.</li>
                <li class="font-semibold">Notifications: Receive real-time notifications about likes, comments, and other activities.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-5 text-center text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold">
        Our social media app is designed to prioritize user experience and security, ensuring that your interactions and data are always protected. Join our community and start sharing your stories today!
    </p>
</div>

